Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages.fromServer

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BuyDVCardError
    message returned if selected development card in the development cards matrix cannot be bought.
    CalamaioErrorMessage
    sent from the server if the action requested by the client during calamaio setting up cannot be performed.
    ChooseLeaderCardMessage
    Message sent from server after the client choose two leader cards out of four.
    EndGameMessage
    EndGameMessage is used from the server to communicate to the client to end the game from his side.
    ErrorMessage
    A generic error message sent from the server to the client
    ErrorStartGameMessage
    Sent from the server if requested start from the client in waiting room cannot be performed
    GameStartedMessage
    Sent from the server after assigning the calamaio and after every player has choosed his first resources
    InitializeCalamaioMessage
    Message sent from server to client to setting up calamaio and player's turn in game
    InWaitingRoomMessage
    Message sent from server to client to start the waiting in the waiting room
    OkMessage
    A generic Server Message to show a positive message to the client
    ParticipantsMessage
    Shows to the client in waiting room the number of participants waiting with him
    SelectActionMessage
    Message sent to the client at the start of a turn.
    ServerLoginErrorMessage
    Sent to the client if there are errors with login credentials, such as a repeated nickname.
    ServerLoginMessage
    Sent to the client to start the log-in process, right after a client thread has been created.
    ServerMessage
    message sent from server TO CLIENT
    ServerMessageFactory
    message factory USED BY the CLIENT, to dynamically get the correct instance the server's message.
    ServerPingMessage
    Server's ping message.
    SinglePlayerActionMessage
    Message sent from server to client to notify about a single player action event.
    StartGameMessage
    Message sent to clients from server to notify about the start of the game.
  • Enum Summary

    ServerMessageType
